    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO : DIRECTOR, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "DATE: 4-22-49",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, LITTLE ROCK",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "SUBJECT: UNKNOWN SUBJECTS;",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "WADE H. HARRISON - INFORMANT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "FORT SMITH, ARKANSAS (4-16-49)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "WADE H. HARRISON, residence address Route 1, Box 293,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Fort Smith, Arkansas, is employed as a Special Delivery messenger by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "the Fort Smith Post Office Department.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "HARRISON stated that at 5:25 p.m., Saturday, April 16, 1949,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "while delivering special delivery mail in Fort Smith, he stopped his",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "automobile at a signal light located at the intersection of North",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Eleventh Street and Grand Avenue. He glanced up at the stop light and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "observed a brilliant object moving in a southeastern direction. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "presumed the object was approximately 2 miles high. He got out of his",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "automobile and pointed up with the suggestion that other automobile",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "drivers, stopped for the signal light, could see the object. He does",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "not know who any of the other people are or what they saw. He was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "obliged to move on after the light changed and the drivers began honking",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "their horns. He watched the object until it was obscured by the line",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "of trees in that section. He estimated he watched it travel some",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "3 or 4 miles before he lost sight of it. He stated the weather was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "clear, visibility was good, and there were no clouds near the object.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "The object made no noise perceptible to HARRISON. However, he commented",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "that he was stopped at an intersection where the traffic was heavy and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "there was considerable noise. He first thought possibly he had seen",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "some type of a reflector on an airplane, but could not locate or hear",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "a plane anywhere.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "HARRISON drove to the 1400 Block of North \"C\" Street, where",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "he observed an Army officer, wearing the insignia of a major or lieutenant",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "colonel, standing back of the officer's automobile. He stopped and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "asked the officer if he had observed the flying object. The officer,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "name unknown to the informant, answered negatively and then remarked,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "\"I am glad other people are also reporting seeing flying objects.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "The officer then related that the day previous, Friday, April 15, 1949,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "while the officer was traveling out of Oklahoma City toward Fort Smith,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "his wife observed a flying object in the sky very similar to that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "described by HARRISON. The officer stated he saw the object too, but",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "furnished no more information.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "status": "blank"
    },
